column5: Sitting here and watching the TV,I turned to see this. Ya it,s Barrie weather.LOL    Gizmo gets excited with fresh snow falls.
March has to come in like a lion before it can go out like a lamb. You have 3 more weeks yet.
Not sure why the vid didnt work
It's working now.They grow fast,nice dog!!looks like he would be lots of fun!
It's not my fault. My winter tires are still on and the snow brush is still in the car.
Bring it on! I love it!!  S.
Snowin in Brampton too. That's nada. It's only the unlucky 13th still have ways to go. We're bound to have one more good dumping yet.
Had just a tee shirt on outside in Red Lake today for a while. I liked it.
We got an inchor so of snow here. Its gonna be cold for the next few days. Real cold at night. Should tighten up the lakes real good  lovin' it! .
I am glad Gizmo likes it and Sinker u would love it here, -43 windchills with just over 4 feet of ice with nothing but clear blue skies   with lots of fish but none biting
